<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> und <expan>etlich<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        brief, die ewch gesandt seyn, <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan> geschikt
                        habt etc., das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wir gern
                                <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und <expan>dank<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan> des mit fleiss. Auch tun wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> zu <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz wir
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemen</expan>, daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        gnedig <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan>, die
                            <expan>kurfürst<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>vom<ex>m</ex></expan> Reyn, mit irem volk
                            <expan>wid<ex>er</ex></expan> die Hussen <pb facs="#facs_310" id="154r"/>kürczlich
                                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>auf</expan> zu land <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        süllen. <add><expan>Sunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan></add>
<expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>,
                        ob die <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>, die wir
                            <expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan> wellen, <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>fürdru<ex>n</ex>g</expan> und hilff icht bedurffen und
                                <expan>beg<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wurd<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz ir in denn umb
                            <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> willen guten
                            <expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan> wellet. Als etc. Denn wo wir
                                <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst
                        etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
<div type="similiter">
<ab>Cettula <expan>int<ex>er</ex>clusa</expan> in
                                papiro<lb/><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir haben disem
                            <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>m</expan> botten <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> guldin
                        zu trinkgelt geben.</ab>
</div>
